  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Twig's Adventure 64 is a tiny 3D collect-a-thon platformer with looks and gameplay inspired by the N64 era, featuring a movement system that is both deep and intuitive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 densely packed worlds with lots of collectibles and secrets.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >a fully explorable hub area</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >an easy and satisfying movement system that also allows for very complex movement tech</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >a secret level</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >controller support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >steam achievements</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Twig's Adventure 64 is a tiny 3D collect-a-thon platformer with looks and gameplay inspired by the N64 era, featuring a movement system that is both deep and intuitive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 densely packed worlds with lots of collectibles and secrets.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >a fully explorable hub area</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >an easy and satisfying movement system that also allows for very complex movement tech</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >a secret level</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >controller support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >steam achievements</p></li></ul>",
